The configuration target shall include query chunk size/overlap, dense model, dense p value, dense candidate limit, embedding floor, SPLADE enablement/model/device/p value, first RRF constant/weights, hydration chunk parameters, reranker model/device/candidate cap, ColBERT enablement, and second RRF constant/weights.
<<<
RELATIONS:
- TYPE: Parent
  VALUE: GHOST-DOC-RETRIEVE-CONFIG-JSON

[REQUIREMENT]
UID: GHOST-DOC-RETRIEVE-CONFIG-UNUSED
