runtime_config document_retrieval keys that are not consumed by the active code, including semantic_stage_max_total_chunks or max_document_chunks_for_a3 where not wired, shall not be described as enforced runtime limits.
<<<
RELATIONS:
- TYPE: Parent
  VALUE: GHOST-DOC-RETRIEVE-CONFIG-JSON

[REQUIREMENT]
UID: GHOST-DOC-RETRIEVE-CONFIG-WEIGHTS
