  VALUE: GHOST-DOC-RETRIEVE-CONFIG-JSON

[REQUIREMENT]
UID: GHOST-DOC-RETRIEVE-EFFECTIVE
STATUS: Draft
TITLE: Effective Retrieval Diagnostics
STATEMENT: >>>
The run shall expose effective query-piece count, dense count, floor-survivor count, sparse mode/count, fusion weights, hydrated count, reranker mode/count, and model identifiers.
<<<
RELATIONS:
- TYPE: Parent
  VALUE: GHOST-DOC-RETRIEVE-ROOT

[REQUIREMENT]
UID: GHOST-DOC-RETRIEVE-ERROR
STATUS: Draft
TITLE: Retrieval Error Integrity
STATEMENT: >>>
Missing dense project stores, invalid vector shapes, incompatible dimensions, sparse candidate misalignment, empty reranker preparation, or invalid configuration shall not produce fabricated successful rankings.
<<<
RELATIONS:
- TYPE: Parent
  VALUE: GHOST-DOC-RETRIEVE-ROOT

